data.text:
800 Fifth Avenue defines elegance and sophistication. Its expansive one-, two-, and three- bedroom residences have unique, well thought out, expansive floorplans, with stainless steel appliances, and high-end fixtures throughout. Amenities abound, including in-house valet service, a state-of-the-art fitness center and yoga studio, a completely redesigned lobby, and an idyllic private garden. Direct access to a myriad of high-end retail, dining and cultural venues as well as Central Park makes 800 Fifth Avenue a one-of-a-kind, exclusive address.

Ever since John Jacob Astor built his grand mansion at 65th Street, Fifth Avenue has been home to New York’s high society. While the stately residences of Astor's day are no more, Fifth Avenue remains the epicenter of elite, world-class lifestyles.
